{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- what came almost naturally to me was that having secured a form of economic independence, it would have been logical for me to try and catch up on the things that I've missed out, in the war years and the-- and the conditions of early life in Australia, dictated by circumstances rather than by choice.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with the help of my good wife, who has been very persuasive, I have applied-- I have applied to every university in Melbourne for acceptance.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have produced my documentation of the graduation at the University of Warsaw, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wrote to Melbourne University.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never got a reply.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to Monash University, and they wouldn't look at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In desperation, I went to La Trobe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And La Trobe wasn't much more interested, even though they had courses for mature-age students, already then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were the third university.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I knew that if I will walk out from that visit to La Trobe, that would end of my dream.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I decided to go and talk to people, from one office to another, in the administrative building, until I knocked at the door of a man, just one door away from the vice chancellor, Dr.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm sure he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Produced my papers, told him what I want to do, and I asked him to help me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He looked at it, and he said, I've got no doubt in my mind that your-- the documents are genuine, that you have finished secondary education, that you have been to university.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you convince me that, almost 40 years later, you are still capable of studying?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can one convince?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you have to give an answer on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
